      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Full episode:\npiped.video/vE15JZRaS6A",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2032489679497421267",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T16:11:16+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "I had an excellent conversation with former U.S. Army Ranger, pastor, and entrepreneur John Lovell @johnlovell275 about faith, masculinity, modern dating and marriage, Gen Z's challenges, raising boys into men, and much more.\n\nOut today on the 'Real Talk with Zuby' podcast!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2032482219755765980",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T15:41:37+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Being completely risk averse guarantees you a life of mediocrity at best.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2032419894021566600",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T11:33:57+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "'Mental health' isn't a good excuse to be a bad person.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2031751834486952434",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T15:19:20+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Kids aspire to whatever society promotes and glorifies. \ud83e\udd37\ud83c\udfff\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\n\n\nDavid Parker (@DavidJPba)\n\n32% of Generation Z's life aspiration is to be a YouTuber/Influencer.\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/DavidJPba/status/2032125074405540317#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2032184363320787127",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T19:58:03+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "If you think that most people's top priority is 'freedom' then you must have been in a coma all through 2020-2022.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2032116948620726439",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T15:30:10+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "After years of complaining about the 'MSM' and their dishonesty, fear mongering, and sensationalism, it's a shame that so many people have taken to social media to run the exact same playbook... just with even lower standards of integrity.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2032108577775665293",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T14:56:54+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Intentionality looks like luck to the uninitiated.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2031990735637991773",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T07:08:38+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "zuby",
      "voiceName": "Zuby",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "I heard I have a cameo appearance in Louis Theroux's latest documentary.\n\nHas anyone seen it? What's the context?",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ZubyMusic/status/2031824031855288668",
